          "type": "text",
          "value": "## math.comb, math.perm, math.factorial\n\nThese are exact integer operations — no floating-point involved:\n\n- `math.comb(n, r)` — combinations: n choose r, order doesn't matter.\n- `math.perm(n, r)` — permutations: n choices for 1st, n-1 for 2nd, ... r slots.\n- `math.factorial(n)` — n! = n × (n-1) × ... × 1; factorial(0) = 1.\n\n```python\nmath.comb(5, 2)    # 10  -- choose 2 from 5\nmath.perm(5, 2)    # 20  -- arrange 2 from 5\nmath.factorial(5)  # 120\n```"
