          "prompt": "Implement two functions:\n\n1. `sorted_insert(sorted_list, value)` — return a **new** sorted list with `value` inserted in the correct position. Use `bisect.insort` on a copy.\n\n2. `search_insert_position(sorted_list, target)` — return the index where `target` is or would be inserted to keep the list sorted. Use `bisect.bisect_left`. This is the answer to LeetCode 35.\n\nNeither function should modify the original list in-place (for `sorted_insert`, work on a copy).",
          "solution": "import bisect\n\ndef sorted_insert(sorted_list, value):\n    # bisect.insort finds the insertion point in O(log n) then shifts in O(n)\n    result = sorted_list[:]\n    bisect.insort(result, value)\n    return result\n\ndef search_insert_position(sorted_list, target):\n    # bisect_left: leftmost valid insertion point, works whether target present or not\n    return bisect.bisect_left(sorted_list, target)\n",
          "tests": "import unittest\nfrom solution import sorted_insert, search_insert_position\n\nclass TestSortedInsert(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_insert_middle(self):\n        self.assertEqual(sorted_insert([1, 3, 5, 7], 4), [1, 3, 4, 5, 7])\n\n    def test_insert_beginning(self):\n        self.assertEqual(sorted_insert([3, 5, 7], 1), [1, 3, 5, 7])\n\n    def test_insert_end(self):\n        self.assertEqual(sorted_insert([1, 3, 5], 9), [1, 3, 5, 9])\n\n    def test_insert_duplicate(self):\n        result = sorted_insert([1, 3, 3, 5], 3)\n        self.assertEqual(result, [1, 3, 3, 3, 5])\n\n    def test_empty_list(self):\n        self.assertEqual(sorted_insert([], 5), [5])\n\nclass TestSearchInsertPosition(unittest.TestCase):\n    def test_present(self):\n        self.assertEqual(search_insert_position([1, 3, 5, 6], 5), 2)\n\n    def test_before_all(self):\n        self.assertEqual(search_insert_position([1, 3, 5, 6], 0), 0)\n\n    def test_after_all(self):\n        self.assertEqual(search_insert_position([1, 3, 5, 6], 7), 4)\n\n    def test_between(self):\n        self.assertEqual(search_insert_position([1, 3, 5, 6], 2), 1)\n\n    def test_empty(self):\n        self.assertEqual(search_insert_position([], 5), 0)\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    unittest.main()\n"
