          "value": "## Capstone: Shortest Path in Grid\n\nThis final exercise synthesizes the entire module:\n- `deque` as FIFO frontier\n- `visited` set populated on enqueue\n- `DIRS` with bounds checking\n- Early termination on reaching the goal\n- Return -1 when the queue is exhausted without reaching the goal\n\nThis is the interview-grade template you write from cold memory."
