          "solution": "def find(parent, x):\n    if parent[x] != x:\n        parent[x] = find(parent, parent[x])\n    return parent[x]\n\ndef union(parent, rank, x, y):\n    rx = find(parent, x)\n    ry = find(parent, y)\n    if rx == ry:\n        return  # already in the same component\n    # attach smaller-rank tree under larger-rank root\n    if rank[rx] < rank[ry]:\n        parent[rx] = ry\n    elif rank[rx] > rank[ry]:\n        parent[ry] = rx\n    else:\n        # tie: pick rx as new root, bump its rank\n        parent[ry] = rx\n        rank[rx] += 1\n",
