          "prompt": "Implement `reconstruct_order_dfs(num_nodes, edges)` — DFS topological sort using the three-color pattern, but written with explicit WHITE/GRAY/BLACK integer constants.\n\nReturn valid topological order or `[]` on cycle.\n\nThis is the same algorithm as the previous exercise, written from scratch to reinforce the three-color convention. A self-loop `(u, u)` is also a cycle.",
