          "solution": "import heapq\nfrom collections import Counter\n\n\ndef top_k_frequent(nums, k):\n    count = Counter(nums)\n    heap = []\n    for num, freq in count.items():\n        heapq.heappush(heap, (freq, num))   # min-heap on frequency\n        if len(heap) > k:\n            heapq.heappop(heap)   # evict lowest frequency; keep top-k\n    return [num for freq, num in heap]\n",
